    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so dishonest to call it \"defiance\" when the outcome is already decided. like, if you knew for a fact that everything was going to burn, wouldnt it be more rational to just not participate? to just step out of the way instead of waiting for the end? it feels like everyone is just choosing to suffer longer for no reason.",
